  - actor: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 454c55e711d4d5b419d643720bde0940, type: 2}
    actorNo: 0
    dialogue:
    - Indeed.
    - It seems the powers I granted each of my Heralds have gone to their heads.
      They have begun interfering in mortal affairs to serve their own ambitions,
      throwing the balance between Life and Death into disarray.
    - If we allow this to continue, the very fabric of our universe could tear itself
      apart. After our souls are agonisingly eviscerated, you, I, and everybody we
      know and love would cease to exist.
    - To avert this fate, I implored the Heralds to see reason. Unfortunately, I
      realised what they were doing too late, and their hubris has already corrupted
      them beyond recognition.
    - "I have grown close to my subordinates\u2026 my friends. But, for the sake
      of humanity, the time for drastic action is now."
