  - actor: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 454c55e711d4d5b419d643720bde0940, type: 2}
    actorNo: 0
    dialogue:
    - I have been watching you for some time now, and see great potential in you.
      Your experience as an assassin in life should serve us both well.
    - However, before I continue, I wish to judge your abilities myself.
    - To aid you, I also wish to bestow two gifts of your own upon you.
    - "Firstly, I offer you a collection of Trickshot Coins, each infused with the
      power to change a projectile\u2019s fate."
    - 'You may use these Reaper Coins to redirect flying projectiles as you see fit.
      Simply fire your weapon [L. Click], and the bullets shall bend to your will. '
    - To practice, I wish for you to use these coins to redirect a single bullet
      to destroy two of my masks.
    - If you fail, do not worry. The second gift I offer you, my own personal Timepiece,
      will allow you to travel through time as you desire.
    - '[R] will rewind time at your discretion.'
